SD=Accounts Receivable
CR=Accounts Receivable Procedure
BQs=Payment CustomerNegotiation Resolution ReceivablesEvaluation
Manage the tracking, chasing and receipt of scheduled payments against issued invoices. For the significant majority accounts are likely to be settled in compliance with established arrangements. For late payment the Service Domain includes actions to negotiate with the customer and handle defaulted payments
A product business unit submits an invoice to a customer for services rendered that requires customer payment from an account not managed by the bank.
This service domain handles accounts receivable for invoices issue by the bank to customers and partners. It includes follow-up and resolution activity for delayed/missed payments
CR - Accounts Receivable Procedure							BQ - Customer Negotiation	BQ Customer Negotiation				BQ - Resolution			BQ - Payment			BQ - Receivables Evaluation			
In	Up	Co	Ec	Ex	Rq	Re	In	Up	Ec	Rq	Re	In	Up	Re	In	Up	Re	In	Up	Ec	Re
InCR Instantiate a new Accounts Receivable Procedure
UpCR Update details relating to Accounts Receivable Procedure
CoCR Control the processing of Accounts Receivable Procedure
EcCR Accept, verify, etc. aspects of Accounts Receivable Procedure processing
ExCR Execute an available automated action for Accounts Receivable Procedure
RqCR Request manual intervention or a decision with respect to Accounts Receivable Procedure
ReCR Retrieve details about any aspect of Accounts Receivable Procedure
InBQ Instantiate a new Customer Negotiation
UpBQ Update details relating to Customer Negotiation
EcBQ Accept, verify, etc. aspects of Customer Negotiation processing
RqBQ Request manual intervention or a decision with respect to Customer Negotiation
ReBQ Retrieve details about any aspect of Customer Negotiation
InBQ Instantiate a new Resolution
UpBQ Update details relating to Resolution
ReBQ Retrieve details about any aspect of Resolution
InBQ Instantiate a new Payment
UpBQ Update details relating to Payment
ReBQ Retrieve details about any aspect of Payment
InBQ Instantiate a new Receivables Evaluation
UpBQ Update details relating to Receivables Evaluation
EcBQ Accept, verify, etc. aspects of Receivables Evaluation processing
ReBQ Retrieve details about any aspect of Receivables Evaluation